Name: TheGunRunner
About the game: GamePlay: Find and retrieve all guns on each level to win. Features: • Levels: Play on city,snow, and desert levels. • Guns: The goal is to retrieve all the guns on each level. • Ammo: For every ammo box retrieved, 1min is added to the timer. • Time: If you don't find all the guns before time runs out. Game over! • Hard: A faced paced game with no save/load.
